snippet.title: Fall Guys Free for All Cinematic Trailer
snippet.description:
Fall Guys Free for All is almost here! 

We can't wait for you to be able to play Fall Guys on all platforms—including the introduction of Nintendo Switch™, Xbox™ and the Epic Games Store™. 

Cross-play and cross-progression also means you’ll now be able to form a party with your friends regardless of the platform they're playing on! With so much to announce,  it really is best to head over to our info-packed blog to get the full scoop on this massive announcement! 

Here's the Free for All Announcement blog: https://www.fallguys.com/news/fall-guys-going-free-on-june-21-launching-on-playstation-nintendo-switch-xbox-and-the-epic-games-store

Watch the official Fall Guys Free for All Cinematic Trailer. For more details on Free for All, visit https://www.fallguys.com/free-for-all

Pre-register for Free for All at https://www.fallguys.com/free-for-all-pre-registration

#FallGuys #FallGuysFreeForAll #FallGuysCinematicTrailer
